page.title: DeadAir ECO T Files
page.t: Consumable schematics used at factories that produce highly advanced wares. They are used to increase the production efficiency of a single production cycle. The amount used depends on the specific ware being produced.

Consumable schematics used at factories that produce militarized wares. They are used to increase the production efficiency of a single production cycle. The amount used depends on the specific ware being produced.

Consumable contracts used to improve conditions for an organized workforce. They are used to increase the production efficiency of a single production cycle. The amount used depends on the specific ware being produced.
